{"thag2.9:0.1":"Theragatha 2.9 ","thag2.9:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.9:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag2.9:0.4":"Gotamattheragatha ","thag2.9:1.1":"“Sukham supanti munayo, ","thag2.9:1.2":"ye itthisu na bajjhare; ","thag2.9:1.3":"Sada ve rakkhitabbasu, ","thag2.9:1.4":"yasu saccam sudullabham. ","thag2.9:2.1":"Vadham carimha te kama, ","thag2.9:2.2":"anana dani te mayam; ","thag2.9:2.3":"Gacchama dani nibbanam, ","thag2.9:2.4":"yattha gantva na socati”ti. ","thag2.9:2.5":"… Gotamo thero …. "}